  "remarks": "Pavel Sluchak is the General Director of OJSC Orsha Aircraft Repair Plant. OJSC Orsha Aircraft Repair Plant is a Belarusian state-owned enterprise that repairs and modernises aircraft. OJSC Orsha Aircraft Repair Plant overhauls and modernises helicopters (Mi-24 and Mi-35) which are used by the Russian Armed Forces in the war of aggression against Ukraine.",
